### PART 5 — AUTOMATION & n8n AUDIT
You mentioned Google Sheets in your prompt, but your site references Supabase. **Commit entirely to Supabase (PostgreSQL).** Google Sheets will fail under concurrent read/writes and rate limits as you scale.

